<section id="candidates_ref">
  <title>ref</title>

  <para>Reference - points to a span of text within the same unit, to which the translation
    candidate is relevant. </para>

  <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> IRI</para>

  <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> undefined</para>

  <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis>
    <olink targetdoc="../elements/candidates/match.xml"
  targetptr="match"><code>&lt;match></code></olink>.</para>

  <itemizedlist>
    <title>Constraints</title>

    <listitem>
      <para>The value of the <olink targetdoc="candidates_ref.xml" targetptr="candidates_ref"
            ><code>ref</code></olink> attribute <glossterm>must</glossterm> point to a span of text
        within the same <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit"
            ><code>&lt;unit></code></olink> element where the <olink
          targetdoc="../elements/candidates/match.xml" targetptr="match"
          ><code>&lt;match></code></olink> is located.</para>
      
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
</section>
